 />\n咁嘅人都係分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ac4dcd03884bc58df9353dfd75dd8c95eaf67c","tid":1516851,"uid":115949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"錢夠日常就可以 做個善良簡單嘅人"},{"pid":"e8208d01921723ddecd706465492b51e441c7437","tid":1516851,"uid":130595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"雖然今次事件唔會經常出現<br />\n但價值觀係根深柢固<br />\n之後再有乜事都會因為價值觀唔同而有新分歧<br />\n<br />\n個問題其實唔係價值觀唔同呢點<br />\n而係你覺得佢因應佢個價值觀所做既選擇令你心寒<br />\n<br />\n你接唔接受到呢份心寒係未來再出現？<br />\n接受到咪唔駛分手<br />\n接受唔到就分手<br />\n<br />\n完全睇你自己<br />\n<br />\n我就唔得既，呢樣已經係良知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313030b4d2b8bd09386fdf11ccd6fafb1689f996","tid":1516851,"uid":35910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"你等佢有日佢唔再咁愛你既時候，佢隨時會出賣你"},{"pid":"490aff38b6a336ae065b5ddf4ed136446a6d0ab0","tid":1516851,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"030854b43765390c18c70a27af24ae9cc48a4072","tid":1516851,"uid":126214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"係 計時炸彈黎 好恐怖 為咗錢咩都做得出 好心寒啊佢答你個啲假設問題嘅答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294e354841ef625ad1b6386b0e873e8113e09593","tid":1516851,"uid":251292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8aafc22a1dd72da738f06f4208b3030cb1238fa","tid":1516851,"uid":291279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b476525f86f0883aca7967b202c3dfcc4d59cab","tid":1516851,"uid":314136,"like":1,"dislike